#aboutme{class: "relative isolate pt-14"}
  %div{class: "mx-auto.max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-x-16 lg:px-8 lg:py-40"}
    %div{class: "max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:flex-auto lg:ml-24"}
      %h1{class: "mt-10 text-pretty text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-7xl"}
        Hello! , My name is Alessandro Chuy
      %h2{class: "mt-4 text-pretty text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-sky-600 sm:text-5xl"}
        Full Stack Web Developer
      %p{class: "mt-8 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 sm:text-xl leading-relaxed"}
        I'm a web developer with a passion for crafting engaging and functional digital experiences. 
        Over the years, I've built a solid foundation in both front-end aesthetics and back-end logic, allowing me 
        to tackle projects that are as visually appealing as they are robust.
      %p{class: "mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 sm:text-xl leading-relaxed"}
        I approach each project with determination and creativity, eager to learn new techniques while refining what I 
        already know. My journey in web development has been one of steady growth and continuous exploration, and I 
        value collaboration and feedback as essential parts of that process.
      .mt-10.flex.items-center.gap-x-6
        %a{href: "mailto:alessandrochuyt@hotmail.com", class: "rounded-lg bg-sky-600 px-5 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-md hover:bg-sky-600 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-sky-600"}
          Contact me

#techstack{class: "mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-8 border border-gray-300 rounded-2xl shadow-xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-10"}
  %h2{class: "text-center font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-3xl sm:text-4xl"}
    Tech stack
  %div{class: "grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 place-items-center gap-10 mt-8"}
    - @techstack.each do |t|
      %div{class: "flex flex-col items-center w-full space-y-3 transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105"}
        = image_tag t[:img], class: "h-24 sm:h-28 w-auto object-contain drop-shadow-md"
        %p{class: "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200"}
          = t[:name]


#contact{class: "mx-auto max-w-7xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-35"}
  %div{class: "bg-gray-50 sm:rounded-lg w-full px-6 py-12 flex justify-center items-center h-115"}
    .max-w-xl
      %h3.text-3xl.font-semibold.text-gray-900
        Let's build something!
      .mt-4.text-xl.text-gray-500
        %p
          Have a great idea? I'm a web developer eager to collaborate on projects that push boundaries and make a difference.
          Let's connect and discuss how we can turn your concept into a powerful online presence.
      .mt-6.flex.justify-center
        %a{href: "mailto:alessandrochuyt@hotmail.com", class: "rounded-md bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-sm focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-sky-600"}
          Contact me

